/a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-277213\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Introduced in March, the tiny Insta260 GO 2 action camera is a self-contained wide-angle cam that packs a lot of features. With stabilization, 120fps slow motion, hyperlapse, and other now-common features, its the size that makes this camera standout.</p><p>The <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/09/insta360-go-2-creates-worlds-smallest-stabilized-waterproof-action-camera/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">original GO 2</a> came with 32GB of internal storage for $299.99. The new GO2 64GB will run $329.99, making the upgrade a no brainer. Both versions come with the charging case (which doubles as a remote control), three mounting accessories, and a lens guard.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/03093147/insta360-g0-2-64gb-action-camera.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/03093147/insta360-g0-2-64gb-action-camera.jpg\" alt=\"insta360 go 2 64gb action camera\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/03093147/insta360-g0-2-64gb-action-camera.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/03093147/insta360-g0-2-64gb-action-camera-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/03093147/insta360-g0-2-64gb-action-camera-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/03093147/insta360-g0-2-64gb-action-camera-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/03093147/insta360-g0-2-64gb-action-camera-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/03093147/insta360-g0-2-64gb-action-camera-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>If youâ€™re looking for an ultra-compact action cam for quick clips to post on social, or want to get some interesting camera angles and POVs (like we did for our Niner JET9 review), check out the full <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/09/insta360-go-2-creates-worlds-smallest-stabilized-waterproof-action-camera/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">tech specs and details in our original story</a>.</p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"1601da0edf322dee69e94fe7bc7b227dc4045889f10b017dba8725f4d8f9d815","category":"Cycling"}